overview.en: JPYT is a digital stable coin minted with a 1:1 mortgage of JPY. The full name of JPY is Japanese Yen, which is a circulating coin in Japan. The partner bank for the JPYT fund certificate is the Royal Bank of the United Arab Emirates.
overview.zh: JPYT是由Libra Xs Foundation发行的去中心化稳定数字货币，其价值与日元1：1锚定。基于区块链技术和智能合约技术发行，保证了透明度，让审计能够高效便捷
